    "quest":{
        "10":{
            "brag":"A small step for your city, but a big leap for the mankind.",
            "title":"First things first"
        },
        "100":{
            "brag":"My Stone production is getting better. How does yours fare?",
            "title":"Humble Beginnings"
        },
        "1000":{
            "brag":"Lumber and Stone bonanza! You better catch up! I'm ahead!",
            "title":"For more Productivity"
        },
        "1100":{
            "brag":"Might and Iron abundance is the key for Mercs. You better watch out! I'm climbing to the top!",
            "title":"For a better Army"
        },
        "1200":{
            "brag":"Sent and received 10 Mercs to an Ally Watch Post. Brothers! Never leave me in vain.",
            "title":"Friendly Mercs"
        },
        "125":{
            "brag":"My Mercs are better equipped now! Think you can match their power?",
            "title":"Better Equipped Army"
        },
        "1300":{
            "brag":"Switf but fragile. Yet no Mercenary can match the destruction they cause... yet.",
            "title":"Recruit Assassins"
        },
        "1400":{
            "brag":"Build up your own gang in WoM, if not, no one will be there for you!",
            "title":"Magnetic Personality"
        },
        "1500":{
            "brag":"Resources are the key.. to everything! I'll soon be better than you!",
            "title":"Hoard more Resources"
        },
        "1600":{
            "brag":"More Mercenaries means more loot! Beware of my numbers!",
            "title":"Build more Barracks"
        },
        "1700":{
            "brag":"Being too careful does not hurt anyone. Stack up the defenses if you want to survive!",
            "title":"Defense First & Always"
        },
        "1800":{
            "brag":"Khamikazees are know to blow issues out of proportion! For me, walls are not a problem anymore!",
            "title":"Power of the Gunpowder!"
        },
        "1900":{
            "brag":"Lumber and Stone carts are arriving by the hunderds, my buildings are stronger. How are YOU doing?",
            "title":"Building Up Quickly"
        },
        "20":{
            "brag":"That was close!",
            "title":"Just in time!"
        },
        "200":{
            "brag":"Statue of Might and Iron Smelter are upgraded to Level 2! Iron from depths of the world, Might from the heavens!",
            "title":"Medieval German Industry"
        },
        "2000":{
            "brag":"Oh, you think YOU can keep up with this?",
            "title":"Industrial Push"
        },
        "2100":{
            "brag":"Gifts are part of the economy, the more friends you have the more potent you are!",
            "title":"Gifting Friends"
        },
        "2200":{
            "brag":"Destroying clans are good for practice. YOU are next on my list!",
            "title":"Meet Demon Clan"
        },
        "2300":{
            "brag":"Towers will have a hard time now! Can you match the destruction the Nubians cause? ",
            "title":"Nubian Wrath"
        },
        "2400":{
            "brag":"You must construct additional Stockpiles!",
            "title":"Stock for hard times"
        },
        "2500":{
            "brag":"A mob of Friends is always useful.",
            "title":"Rise thourgh Help"
        },
        "2600":{
            "brag":"Grand cities require grand defenses. Think you can match these towers?",
            "title":"Upgrade Security"
        },
        "2650":{
            "brag":"This is a war game. Be prepared for offense and defense!",
            "title":"Get Ready for War!"
        },
        "2675":{
            "brag":"No one can stand up to the destruction i have caused. Think you can endure it?",
            "title":"By the Numbers"
        },
        "2700":{
            "brag":"City standards are increased! Think you can build as much as i can?",
            "title":"Higher Standards"
        },
        "2800":{
            "brag":"Resources are ready to push construction and invade! Do you have enough to match my power?",
            "title":"Hoard of Legends"
        },
        "2900":{
            "brag":"My Mercenaries are not alone at the Battlefield, how do yours without support?",
            "title":"Artillery Support"
        },
        "30":{
            "brag":"Digitized Infantry is the key.",
            "title":"Rookie of Destruction"
        },
        "300":{
            "brag":"Spring Cleaning checklist ",
            "title":"Weeder Blues"
        },
        "3000":{
            "brag":"If you give it to me I'll give it to you, as long as you want.",
            "title":"Fair Trade"
        },
        "3100":{
            "brag":"Saving space in Barracks can be donbe with one click!",
            "title":"Execution saves the Space"
        },
        "3200":{
            "brag":"These Mercenaries are called Ravagers for a good reason, watch the cities after they enter!",
            "title":"Recruit Ravager"
        },
        "3300":{
            "brag":"Gift'em all! It will benefit you in the long run!",
            "title":"Be like a Rockstar"
        },
        "3400":{
            "brag":"Granduer comes with Resources. Can you hoard as much as i can?",
            "title":"Obsessive Hoarder"
        },
        "350":{
            "brag":"Brutes are on a rampage, when there are many! Hire them en masse!",
            "title":"Use Brute Force"
        },
        "3500":{
            "brag":"From now on, the last thing the sorry defenders will see will be the Painblowers. Watch out! ",
            "title":"Recruit Painblower"
        },
        "3600":{
            "brag":"My City has First World Standards! ",
            "title":"Like a Boss!"
        },
        "3700":{
            "brag":"!!!PLEASE REPORT WHEN YOU SEE THIS. WITH A SCREENSHOT!!!",
            "title":"You've got mail!"
        },
        "3800":{
            "brag":"Now watch the attackers burn! Flamer is better than anything to Mercenaries en masse!",
            "title":"Flaming Defense"
        },
        "3900":{
            "brag":"Loot will flow! Better recruit Sneak Peek fast, before enemies have an advantage!",
            "title":"Et tu, bro?"
        },
        "40":{
            "brag":"Green like grass.",
            "title":"Ready to conscript"
        },
        "400":{
            "brag":"Bombard Tower will take care of the weak enemies. Have you taken the same precautions?",
            "title":"The Might Strategist"
        },
        "4000":{
            "brag":"All loot are belong to me! You better fight hard to loot as much as i can!",
            "title":"Elite Standards"
        },
        "4050":{
            "brag":"Stock like there is no tomorrow, i bet no one has this much resources!",
            "title":"Obsessive Hoarder"
        },
        "4100":{
            "brag":"If you can't spot the sucker Clans, then you are the sucker!",
            "title":"Clan Homicide!"
        },
        "4200":{
            "brag":"Towers? They are not a problem anymore! With Mongolians here, you can deploy them and forget!  ",
            "title":"Mongolian Invasion"
        },
        "4300":{
            "brag":"Over-protection does not hurt anyone, especially while your enemies lurk at your gates!",
            "title":"Over-protection"
        },
        "4400":{
            "brag":"All these resources will be the end of my enemies, watch out for my Hordes and invicible defenses!",
            "title":"Master Harvester"
        },
        "450":{
            "brag":"It is always better to be well informed. Build your own Pigeon Post and get the latest intel!",
            "title":"Now, whats this?"
        },
        "4500":{
            "brag":"Ancient warriors join the ranks! Can you match their epicness? Bet not!",
            "title":"Egyptian Power"
        },
        "4600":{
            "brag":"Look at the gifts i give!",
            "title":"Philantrophia"
        },
        "4700":{
            "brag":"More space for resources = More possible loot. How much more can you have?",
            "title":"Never Ending Hoard"
        },
        "4800":{
            "brag":"Bear responsibilities and send your Bearwolf first! Bet your Mercenaries will be unhurt!",
            "title":"Hear him roar!"
        },
        "4900":{
            "brag":"My Beast is well fed and healthy. Means you will have a hard time defending!",
            "title":"Petting the Beast"
        },
        "50":{
            "brag":"Ready to eat arrows and make money.",
            "title":"Whose army?"
        },
        "500":{
            "brag":"Stockpiles can store more resources for later use. How much can you collect?",
            "title":"Save your Resources"
        },
        "5000":{
            "brag":"State of art Mercenary equipment and Towers are ready. Come on!",
            "title":"Like the Maginot Line"
        },
        "5100":{
            "brag":"Now, my Mercenaries are undying! Better evade me while you can!",
            "title":"Medic!"
        },
        "5200":{
            "brag":"When the last glimpse of hope is gone, your brothers will always run!",
            "title":"Alliance for Victory"
        },
        "5300":{
            "brag":"Come get some! My Watchposts are full now!",
            "title":"Men the Ranks!"
        },
        "5400":{
            "brag":"It's a bird... it's a plane... It's Hezarfen! Your towers will burn with death from above!",
            "title":"Death from above"
        },
        "5500":{
            "brag":"I have many Beasts at my disposal. Your city wont be a match for my ever-changing tactics.",
            "title":"Leash that beast!"
        },
        "5600":{
            "brag":"Ultimate damage to the seemingly invicible cities! Prepare your defenses!",
            "title":"Mammoth Power"
        },
        "5700":{
            "brag":"Clans are razed, and their resources are in my hands. You are next on the list!",
            "title":"Clan Genocide"
        },
        "5800":{
            "brag":"Expand your brotherhood, help friends, gain RP; it's that easy!",
            "title":"Great Alliance"
        },
        "5900":{
            "brag":"Defenses can kill what they can see. Yours will be certainly helpless against the blitz of the Sappers!",
            "title":"Death from the Depths"
        },
        "60":{
            "brag":"Improved harvests are now available with red lumberjack shirts!",
            "title":"Lumberjack"
        },
        "600":{
            "brag":"This City can have better and more Buildings now! I'm stronger now!",
            "title":"Access Higher Technology"
        },
        "6000":{
            "brag":"My ultimate weapons have grown! You think you can stop them?",
            "title":"Über-Beasts"
        },
        "601":{
            "hint":"Click on the Lumber Blade to harvest lumber "
        },
        "602":{
            "hint":"Click on the Lumber Blade to upgrade it"
        },
        "6100":{
